  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the safety, tolerance and efficacy of three different dosage regimens of
      Amphotericin B Lipid Complex (ABLC) compared to Fungizone (Amphotericin B) in patients with
      AIDS and cryptococcal meningitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
